Package: tweets2earth
Type: Package
Title: plot or stream tweets' location and created time to Google Earth
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-05-29
Author: Jabber Cruncher
Maintainer: John Coene <jcoenep@gmail.com>
Description: Comes with two functions, one to plot tweets, typically obtained
    from the twitteR package, onto Google Earth. The other to stream tweets, using
    the streamR package, onto Google Earth.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    streamR,
    sp,
    spacetime,
    plotKML
Suggests:
    ROAuth,
    RCurl
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
URL: https://github.com/JohnCoene/tweets2earth
BugReports: https://github.com/JohnCoene/tweets2earth/issues
